Squirrelmail Plugin OpenVISPadmin
*********************************

This Software is Based on SMpostfixadmin with some little modifications 
to handle OpenVISP Admin

version 0.3-1.4 01/29/04

Postfixadmin - Postfixadmin+MySQL DB plugin for SquirrelMail

Author: Florian Kimmerl info@spacekoeln.de>

The Postfixadmin SquirrelMail plugin let users change their virtual alias,
vacation status/message and password if you are using the great postfixadmin
tool from http://high5.net/postfixadmin

The Initial Developer of the Original postfixadmin Code is Mischa Peters.
Portions created by Mischa Peters are Copyright (c) 2002, 2003, 2004.
All Rights Reserved.

REQUIREMENTS

o SquirrelMail 1.4x

o A working Mail-System "Virtual Domains and Users with postfix+Courier-IMAP+MySQL" See http://high5.net/howto/

o POSTFIXADMIN version 2.0.0 or higher. See http://high5.net/postfixadmin/

o This plugin only uses the postfixadmin database


INSTALLATION

o These directions assume you already have a working install of postfix
  with courier-imap,MySQL, postfixadmin, SquirrelMail and the database installed.

o Unpack in the plugins directory of your SM installation.

o Copy config.php.dist to config.php and edit config.php to change the
  Database Config, the Language and enable/disable virtual vacation.

o Enable the postfixadmin plugin.


